shampoo /ʃæmˈpuː/

(shampooing,shampooed,shampoos) 

1. N-MASS Shampoo is a soapy liquid that you use for washing your hair. 洗发液 

例： ...a bottle of shampoo. …一瓶洗发水。 

2. V-T When you shampoo your hair, you wash it using shampoo. 用洗发水洗 

例： Shampoo your hair and dry it. 用洗发水洗洗你的头发，然后把头发弄干。

